.input-group
  = form.text_field( \
      :hidden_link,
      { class: 'form-control',
        placeholder: 'Click the Refresh button to generate a link',
        readonly: true,
        data: { story_target: 'hiddenLinkInput' }})
  span.input-group-btn
    button.hidden-link__refresh.btn.btn-default {
      type="button"
      style="border-radius: 0; border-left: 0"
      data-controller="tooltip"
      data-tooltip-options-value={ title: 'Refresh', container: 'body', placement: 'top' }.to_json
      data-action="story#refreshHiddenLink" }
      i.fa.fa-refresh
  span.input-group-btn
    button.hidden-link__copy.btn.btn-default {
      type="button"
      class=('disabled' if story.hidden_link.blank?)
      data-controller="tooltip"
      data-tooltip-options-value={ title: 'Copy', container: 'body', placement: 'top' }.to_json
      data-story-target="hiddenLinkCopyBtn" }
      i.fa.fa-clipboard
span.help-block style="margin-bottom: 0"
  | Allows for early access without regard to publication status. Refreshing the link will automatically expire any previous links.